	// option
	"synced.option.title": "<header>Resynced Configurations</>",
	"synced.option.titlet": "Welcome to Resynced ! A mod that extend the base game with functionality and option through configurable module.\n\nTo see settings, you need to start a game with the mod enabled.\nAlso on multiplayer game, only host can see and change settings.",
	"synced.option.languages": "<gl>Languages :</>",
	"synced.option.languagest": "Only <bl>English</> and <bl>French</> are officially translated.\n<rl>Important :</> <hl>Resynced</> use 'id' instead of 'string' for translation, meaning all languages use <bl>English</> text as default to avoid missing string !",
	"synced.option.content": "<gl>Content :</>",
	"synced.option.contentt": "- <bl>Bot Speed</>, allow you to increase the speed of your bots.\n- <bl>Bug Wave</>, wich add a custom bug invasion and event.\n- <bl>Energy Manager</>, allow you to change power production and transfer range.\n- <bl>Fast Production</>, increase the speed of all production and research.\n- <bl>Infinite Resource Node</>, allow you to use resource node forever.\n- <bl>Mining Upgrade</>, increase mining efficiency and range.\n- <bl>Puzzle Hacker</>, add an item to bypass minigames.\n- <bl>Better Stack</>, allow you to increase all stack size.\n- <bl>Custom UI</>, A rework of in game UI, smaller and compact. <rl>WIP</>\n<rl>Content has changed and contain a lot more content, meaning this part will be rewrite soon to be more explicit.</>",
	"synced.option.warn": "<gl>Compatibility :</>",
	"synced.option.warnt": "<hl>Resynced is save safe and can be enabled, disabled, removed or added at any time. ( Any Resynced items / frames / techs will be removed by the game )</>",
	
	// ui
	"synced.ui.title": "<header>Resynced Configurations ( v%s )</>", // removed
	"synced.ui.description": "Welcome to Resynced ! A mod that extend the base game with functionality\nand option through configurable module.\n\nTo see settings, you need to start a game with the mod enabled.\nAlso on multiplayer game, only host can see and change settings.\n\n<gl>About supported languages :</>\nOnly <bl>English</> and <bl>French</> are officially translated.\n<rl>Important :</> <hl>Resynced</> use 'id' instead of 'string' for translation, meaning all\nlanguages use <bl>English</> text as default to avoid missing string !\n\n<gl>What is included in the mod ?</>\n- <bl>Bot Speed</>, allow you to increase the speed of your bots.\n- <bl>Bug Wave</>, wich add a custom bug invasion and event.\n- <bl>Energy Manager</>, allow you to change power production and transfer range.\n- <bl>Fast Production</>, increase the speed of all production and research.\n- <bl>Infinite Resource Node</>, allow you to use resource node forever.\n- <bl>Mining Upgrade</>, increase mining efficiency and range.\n- <bl>Puzzle Hacker</>, add an item to bypass minigames.\n- <bl>Better Stack</>, allow you to increase all stack size.\n- <bl>Custom UI</>, A rework of in game UI, smaller and compact. <rl>WIP</>\n\n<hl>Resynced is save safe and can be enabled, disabled, removed or added at any</>\n<hl>time. ( Any Resynced items / frames / techs will be removed by the game )</>", // removed
	"synced.ui.help": "- Chaque modules sera désactivé de base.\n- Passez la souris sur les éléments pour afficher des infobulles.\n- Le bouton <gl>Appliquer les modifications</> n'est pas obligatoire mais il est plus rapide, Si vous ne l'utilisez pas, vous devrez sauvegarder et recharger manuellement pour appliquer les modifications !\n- Pour ajouter une traduction, veuillez vous référer à <gl>'Resynced/translations/en.json'</>.\n- Pour ajouter vos propres options de mod dans <hl>Resynced</>, consultez <gl>'Resynced/ModSample.zip'</>.",
	"synced.ui.apply": "Appliquer les modifications",
	"synced.ui.applyt": "Cela créera une sauvegarde temporaire (nommée <gl>'Resynced_TEMP'</>) et la chargera pour appliquer vos paramètres.",
